            Before throwing money at the problem, it helps to understand what's actually causing
            your laptop to crawl. Here are the culprits we see most often at our repair shop in
            Harold Hill:
          </p>

          <div class="numbered-card">
            <div class="numbered-card-number space-font" style="color: var(--starlight-white);">
              1
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3
                class="space-font"
                style="color: var(--starlight-white); font-size: 18px; margin: 0 0 12px;"
              >
                Traditional Hard Drive (HDD) Instead of SSD
              </h3>
              <p style="margin: 0;">
                This is the single biggest factor affecting laptop speed. If your laptop has a
